NAME: Afiqa Nolla Dianissa
REVIEW: Di bagian indoor ada banyak meja, tapi untuk outdoor cuma sepetak di teras bagian depan. Smoking room hanya bisa di outdoor. Di indoor ada meja biliard kecil bebas bisa main.

NAME: damar kahono
REVIEW: Terletak di area phoenix hotel, areanya tidak terlalu besar. ada meja billiardnya.

NAME: Joseph Hahn
REVIEW: The trainee bartender “forgot” to put any alcohol in the drinks and then when it was brought to her attention, she only put a thimble of rum in each drink (not a shot cup, but the metal base of the shot cup). Drinks obviously weaker than any I’ve ever had. And at 120,000 per drink it is totally unacceptable. We are hotel guests at the Phoenix and would advise other guests to go somewhere else.

NAME: Yoseph Kwantita
REVIEW: Nice and cozy bar inside The Phoenix Hotel by MGallery Sofitel Jogjakarta . The design of the bar is heritage . Inside you will find big selection of wine and very nice signature cocktail Gin Sling . You can enjoy while youre in town . Recomended! Bar yang sangat nyaman untuk hangout ada meja billiard

NAME: Simon
REVIEW: Nice bar with elegant ambience. Great cocktails - they made a fantastic rum sour. Staff friendly and eager to please

NAME: Lelembut 21
REVIEW: A nice bar for hang out. Affordable price here.
